    @JSON(strict=true)
public class GuestbookModelImpl
extends com.liferay.portal.model.impl.BaseModelImpl<com.liferay.docs.guestbook.model.Guestbook>
implements com.liferay.docs.guestbook.model.GuestbookModel
    The base model implementation for the Guestbook service. Represents a row in the "GB_Guestbook" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This implementation and its corresponding interface GuestbookModel exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in GuestbookImpl.

    Author:
    benyedai
    See Also:
    GuestbookImpl, Guestbook, GuestbookModel, Serialized Form
